24:37.076 --> 24:40.179 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ANDREW, Ukraine: I decided to be
useful here
at least.

24:40.212 --> 24:44.550 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Andrew, who also
refused to
give his last name, is former
Soviet special

24:44.583 --> 24:47.820 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
forces. He says he came here to
train a ragtag
army.

24:47.853 --> 24:49.755 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Were you sent here by Russia?

24:49.788 --> 24:56.895 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANDREW: No. No. I'm a volunteer,
so nobody
-- nobody pay me something. I
don't see professionally

24:56.929 --> 25:02.701 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
