see drivers.

25:02.735 --> 25:05.237 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Come, guys. Let's go.

25:05.270 --> 25:09.908 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Their base used
to be a local
school. They resist Ukraine's
alliance with

25:09.942 --> 25:14.913 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Europe. They align with Russia.
And as the
war persists, their desire to
separate grows.

25:14.947 --> 25:19.651 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): Once
an army targets
its own people, they become the
enemy.

25:19.685 --> 25:22.321 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ANDREW: How we can be in one
state now?

25:22.354 --> 25:24.957 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: So you have to
separate now?

25:24.990 --> 25:27.826 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ANDREW: Sure. They have to
separate.

25:27.860 --> 25:34.199 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: The front is
280-miles-long.
To get to the village of
Spartak, we needed

25:34.233 --> 25:37.536 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
