25:37.569 --> 25:41.573 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On this front line, Anya, who
also declined
to give her last name, leads
what she calls

25:41.607 --> 25:46.412 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
an infantry brigade. The
professional Russian
soldiers here whom U.S.
officials say number

25:46.445 --> 25:48.814 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
