what is the
risk here?

25:52.718 --> 25:56.622 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ANYA, Ukraine (through
translator): Total
risk. We're now walking in their
snipers'

25:56.655 --> 26:00.225 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
