26:19.611 --> 26:31.924 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator): I will
take him
out quickly.

26:31.957 --> 26:38.030 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN (through translator): Are
you kidding?

26:38.063 --> 26:39.264 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
