26:39.298 --> 26:42.935 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ANYA (through translator): Let's
go! Let's
go! Stay down.

26:42.968 --> 26:47.606 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Like many of
these fighters,
Anya's not a trained soldier.
