is fighting with us following
NATO orders.

26:58.083 --> 27:02.154 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They are nothing on their own.
You are writing
that I'm a blonde separatist who
will come

27:02.187 --> 27:05.290 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
