Yes, I will
do just that.

27:05.324 --> 27:08.193 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Are you willing
to die for
this cause?

27:08.227 --> 27:11.430 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANYA (through translator): Yes,
of course,
I'm ready to die for my home. I
will not let

27:11.463 --> 27:15.501 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
