Teenage girls spend
Saturday afternoons with Russian
Kalashnikovs.

27:42.261 --> 27:46.598 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The average Russian soldier
needs more than
10 seconds to do this;
15-year-old Katerina

27:46.632 --> 27:48.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
