27:48.433 --> 27:53.005 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KATERINA, Ukraine (through
translator): Since
I was little, I preferred
playing football

27:53.038 --> 27:54.840 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
