27:54.873 --> 28:01.013 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Next up, Soviet
hazmat suits.
Their teacher, Sergey Fomchenko,
is a former

28:01.046 --> 28:03.015 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Soviet soldier and police
officer.

28:03.048 --> 28:05.450 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SERGEY FOMCHENKO, Former Soviet
Soldier (through
translator): Why, when we look
toward Russia,

28:05.484 --> 28:10.689 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
