28:12.591 --> 28:18.297 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Upstairs, he
shows me where
a rocket struck this school.
Ukraine and Russia

28:18.330 --> 28:23.535 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
have agreed Donetsk should
eventually reintegrate
into Ukraine. But everyone we
spoke to rejected

28:23.569 --> 28:24.503 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
that.

28:24.536 --> 28:27.272 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Would you ever be able to go
back to Ukraine?

28:27.306 --> 28:31.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SERGEY FOMCHENKO (through
