28:37.983 --> 28:48.026 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: So the training
continues.
They know their AKs by heart.

28:48.026 --> 28:54.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: So the training
continues.
