28:54.633 --> 28:59.671 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When they're not training,
they're proselytizing.
The Donetsk military is short on
recruits.

28:59.705 --> 29:05.010 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So the girls hand out recruiting
flyers to
fighting-age males, anyone
between 18 and

29:05.043 --> 29:10.816 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
55. Katerina also rejects
returning to Ukraine,
because of what this war has
forced her to

29:10.849 --> 29:12.618 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
