29:12.651 --> 29:14.386 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KATERINA (through translator):
There was a
shell in my apartment block.
Everything was

29:14.419 --> 29:18.824 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
