29:26.264 --> 29:32.804 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Downtown, city workers whose
salaries are
paid by Russia look after public
gardens.

29:32.838 --> 29:38.377 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In supermarkets, the shelves are
stocked with
Russian products. The only
currency accepted

29:38.410 --> 29:44.082 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
