distraction

30:11.276 --> 30:21.086 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and ideology.

30:21.119 --> 30:25.991 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But this city is an orphan. The
Donetsk People's
Republic was birthed with the
help of Russian

30:26.024 --> 30:30.295 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
