here.

30:45.177 --> 30:48.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALEXANDR GORYAKIN, Ukraine
(through translator):
The best option in terms of
opportunities

30:48.447 --> 30:51.917 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
