leave the front
lines, life is even more
difficult.

31:07.866 --> 31:12.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Valentina Nikolayevna sleeps in
her cellar
because she's scared of
shelling. She hasn't

31:12.971 --> 31:16.274 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
