in two years.

31:16.308 --> 31:18.243 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Has it been worth it?

31:18.276 --> 31:21.546 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VALENTINA NIKOLAYEVNA, Ukraine
(through translator):
During the second World War, it
took us, the

31:21.580 --> 31:27.219 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
