31:28.653 --> 31:32.157 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Can you just
describe how difficult
life has gotten?

31:32.190 --> 31:34.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VALENTINA NIKOLAYEVNA (through
translator):
I would have never believed it
if two years

31:34.826 --> 31:43.802 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
