going to
live in a basement. Very hard.

31:43.835 --> 31:50.342 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Nearby, this is
all that's
left of the Donetsk Airport. It
was built

31:50.375 --> 31:56.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
