these streets.
They invited me in their home.
Her husband,

32:13.799 --> 32:18.270 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Zakharoff Pavlovich, grew up in
this house.
A Ukrainian rocket landed in
their backyard.

32:18.303 --> 32:21.807 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ZAKHAROFF PAVLOVICH, Ukraine
(through translator):
There were so many rockets. We
just heard

32:21.840 --> 32:23.842 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
