32:23.875 --> 32:29.581 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: This collection
of bricks used
to be their bomb shelter. They
stay because

32:29.614 --> 32:33.919 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
